{
  "texts": [
    "Through analyzing the advantages and disadvantages of different models on different tasks, two ensemble learning models based on the existing models are proposed to be applied to three NLP tasks.",
    "Experiments demonstrate that our proposed ensemble learning models outperform a single model based on the transformer model.",
    "Structure of the paperIn \"Introduction\" section, we study the research questions and motivations.",
    "In \"Background\" section, we introduced the research background, and described the research task and the model used.",
    "In \"Review of related works\" section, we sorted out the related literature."
  ]
}